<p>[June 1918]<br/> 30 Sun<br/>Vivtar to the Canadians<br/>1 July Mon<br/>The American lassies are "IT", very pretty girls<br/>2 Tues<br/>Rumors flying about that we are preparing for a big battle, on the "Somme front.<br/>3 Wed<br/>To day I was marked fir for Duty, it is hard to leave</p>
